graph.description: Resource model created for the Florida Public Archaeology Network "Heritage Monitoring Scouts" program to represent Historic Structure resources. Designed to hold all qualitative information from the Florida Master Site File shapefile export of "Florida Structure" resources, as well as HMS-specific attributes, such as site visit evaluations.
